Kafka File Messenger

-This project used custom Kafka serializers and simulates sending and receiving of a file through Kafka


Kafka Sender

--Sends a file through Kafka

Main Class :KafkaFileSender

USAGE : 
-b|--broker-list :Comma separated list of brokers
-t|--topic :topic name
-f|--file :absolute path of file to be sent
--help print help";

Example : 

java KafkaFileSender -b localhost:9091 -t fileTopic -f Message.txt
	
